data.description: Welcome to this spacious home within walking distance to Lake Saunders!  Relax on the spacious front veranda or the enclosed back lanai to overlook the flower garden.  The cathederal ceilings greet you with a majestic precense when you enter the house!  The Master bedroom is conveniently located downstairs while the remaing three are upstairs. There's a hideaway room under the stairs as well! Located just minutes from downtown Tavares “The Seaplane City” & Mount Dora. This neighborhood is also home to the local YMCA, and a short three-minute drive to the  Advent Health Hospital and local shopping plazas.
